SUMMARY:Pet Portrait Sip & Design at Eureka Heights
DESCRIPTION:Join us for a fun afternoon of painting your pet’s portrait while sipping on a delicious selection at the Eureka Heights! \n🐾PET PORTRAIT SIP & DESIGN! 🐾 \nCalling all pet lovers and art enthusiasts! Join us for the most adorable creative event at @eurekaheights! \n🎨 What’s Included:\n• All painting materials\n• Guided pet portrait session\n• Tons of fun! \nPlease send a picture of your pet after signing up or bring your favorite four-legged friend (in photo form) and create a masterpiece you’ll treasure forever! No painting experience is necessary – just bring your creativity and be ready to have fun!\nEvent Link
URL:https://www.eurekaheights.com/event/pet-portrait-sip-design-at-eureka-heights-2026-06-26/
LOCATION:Tap Room\, 941 W 18TH ST.\, Houston\, TX\, 77008\, United States
CATEGORIES:Tap Room
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/webp:https://www.eurekaheights.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/image-1.webp
END:VEVENT
