LAST-MODIFIED:20260605T081504Z
UID:9792-1782565200-1782579600@www.eurekaheights.com
SUMMARY:Houston Plant Swap/ AJL Adoption Event
DESCRIPTION:Calling all plant lovers\, join us for our monthly plant swap and market! Come grab a pint and go home with all the plants. This month we’ll be also featuring two local adoption agencies with adoptable cats and dogs from Animal Justice League and Spring Branch Rescue
URL:https://www.eurekaheights.com/event/houston-plant-swap-ajl-adoption-event-2026-06-27/
LOCATION:Tap Room\, 941 W 18TH ST.\, Houston\, TX\, 77008\, United States
CATEGORIES:Tap Room
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://www.eurekaheights.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/EH-Events-Calendar-June-2026-3.png
END:VEVENT
