SUMMARY:Laces Out Run Club
DESCRIPTION:Every Thursday at 5:30 and 6:30 PM\, our Laces Out Run Club members start on a route of their choosing\, ranging from a 2\, 3.5\, 5\, or 8 mile run. After their run\, they receive $2 off beers the rest of the evening! \nREWARDS \n🎽 10 runs: EH headband\n🎽 25 runs: Laces Out shirt\n🎽 50 runs: Running shorts\n🎽 100 runs: Singlet \n  \n  \n  \n 
